 />\n大集匯就真係好難諗用咩類型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T05:21:12.000Z","msg":"我覺得大集匯既就可以用火影隻game同埋spiderman嗰種方式咁<br />\n有唔同既任，有群戰有打boss有潛入有解難咁有唔同既任務<br />\n用end game做一part既例子咁<br />\n就由一開始係iron man要玩一啲解難先搵到翻去過去既方法<br />\n之後回到過去嗰度就差唔多每個人都可以有一部分，E.g.CA打自己，Iron man做潛入偷魔方咁<br />\n之後就到三人打boss，再之後就群戰打兵保護手套<br />\n最後就彈手指<br />\n當然呢個只係成隻game既一部分<br />\n其實最好既就係Avg 1包埋之前個人電影出一隻<br />\nAvg2既同Avg1中間既又一隻<br />\nAvg3,4同之前中間既又一隻咁<br />\n一隻遊戲個長度就最fit"},{"pid":"fba36e61452134881b78192d2990dc9bda7a354b","tid":1145472,"uid":12252,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"63956d90b9eb07647fb8bd0f0c3bc88d44a0dae4","tid":1145472,"uid":202828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T19:27:24.000Z","msg":"你叫黑寡婦，mantis嗰堆點樣無雙法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />頂多咪一對三"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T05:32:40.000Z","msg":"三國無雙都有諸葛亮用啦"},{"pid":"533a922c9e4beaec170cd8e38ebe976dd8570f2b","tid":1145472,"uid":1654,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"fba36e61452134881b78192d2990dc9bda7a354b","tid":1145472,"uid":12252,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"63956d90b9eb07647fb8bd0f0c3bc88d44a0dae4","tid":1145472,"uid":202828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T19:27:24.000Z","msg":"你叫黑寡婦，mantis嗰堆點樣無雙法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />頂多咪一對三"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T05:32:40.000Z","msg":"三國無雙都有諸葛亮用啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T05:38:52.000Z","msg":"激光炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0d9eb2d38a83303720d5230c7779228c610d640","tid":1145472,"uid":75042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T06:05:08.000Z","msg":"如果佢呢排咁樣出一隻game應該賣500都大把人搶"},{"pid":"303837a6592c1531a6ccaa5853fccc8e1fcd0598","tid":1145472,"uid":37759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":